==English==

{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
'''the [[philosopher|philosopher’s]] [[stone]]'''
===Alternative spellings===
*philosophers’ stone<!-- often capitalised -->

#(''[[alchemy]]'') A [[substance]] able to turn [[base metal]]s into [[gold]] or [[silver]], usually by means of the application and distillation of another substance, usually mercury.

